title: James Gang - Jesse Come Home [1976]
description:
James Gangs final recording, Jesse Come Home from 1976, which referred to the band&#039;s namesake, the outlaw Jesse James, with the collaboration of early member Phil Giallombardo, who rejoined along with new guitarist/vocalist Bob Webb. Jimmy Fox was the only remaining member of the original quintet when they disbanded in 1977.
